Scripted button. Resizes the width of the stack in which it is placed to one of two sizes contained in custom properties stored on the button:

cContractedStackWidth
cExpandedStackWidth

The button references 2 images. These are set as the icon and the hiliteIcon of the button.

Note that this control requires the "Revolution Icons" image library to be tranferred to your stack using Distribution Builder when you are preparing your stack for distribution.